➜香港「囍帖街茶冰室」来静安寺了！港点个个讨口彩
http://www.sohu.com/a/414830494_789206	31638
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200825/4927d62ea267446c83e583cb2fd20c9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200825/f0d31390a84e4e56a0f36818b33826f4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200825/8c7c82cb3d1540b08472f028c91655b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200825/58e30da66efb467186b53fa8b0f94c99.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
